data.description: Open the door and see what this wonderful one-story home has to offer, located in heart of Converse. Great open floor plan with large single living area. Very accommodating dining area that's right off the fabulous kitchen with plenty of cabinet and countertop space. Comfortable size primary bedroom and 2 generous sized secondary bedrooms. All of this, but now step out back to your own relaxing getaway. Nice size back yard, cover patio and hot tub! Plenty of privacy, good landscaping and excellent storage shed.    What a great way to start out in your new home, with built-in LOVE!
